<h3 id="2-配置发布设置"><a href="#2-配置发布设置" class="headerlink" title="2.配置发布设置"></a>2.配置发布设置</h3><p>如果你一切都配置好了，发布上传很容易，一句hexo d就搞定，当然关键还是你要把所有东西配置好。<br>首先，ssh key肯定要配置好。<br>其次，配置_config.yml中有关deploy的部分：<br>正确写法：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: git@github.com:liuxianan&#x2F;liuxianan.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

