<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: github</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;liuxianan&#x2F;liuxianan.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">后面一种写法是hexo2.x的写法，现在已经不行了，无论是哪种写法，此时直接执行hexo d的话一般会报如下错误：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Deployer not found: github 或者 Deployer not found: git</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">原因是还需要安装一个插件：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
